<article id="post-152" class="post-152 post type-post status-publish format-image hentry category-uncategorized post_format-post-format-image">
	<div class="blog-item-wrap">
				<a href="http://markfern.me/2015/09/voip-at-home-and-250-in-your-pocket/" title="VOIP at Home and $250 in your pocket." >
			 				</a>
		<div class="post-inner-content">
			<header class="entry-header page-header">

				<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://markfern.me/2015/09/voip-at-home-and-250-in-your-pocket/" rel="bookmark">VOIP at Home and $250 in your pocket.</a></h1>

								<div class="entry-meta">
					<span class="posted-on"><i class="fa fa-calendar"></i> <a href="http://markfern.me/2015/09/voip-at-home-and-250-in-your-pocket/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2015-09-30T12:44:26+00:00">September 30, 2015</time><time class="updated" datetime="2015-10-01T08:44:23+00:00">October 1, 2015</time></a></span><span class="byline"> <i class="fa fa-user"></i> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://markfern.me/author/fernmark/">Mark</a></span></span>				<span class="comments-link"><i class="fa fa-comment-o"></i><a href="http://markfern.me/2015/09/voip-at-home-and-250-in-your-pocket/#respond">Leave a comment</a></span>
				
				
				</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
							</header><!-- .entry-header -->

						<div class="entry-content">

				<p>A while back a friend asked me how I did this so he could too. For cable modem subscribers, the savings is about $250 per year. You also get greater control over blocked numbers, forwarding, and voicemail.  I purchased an <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00BUV7C9A/ref=cm_sw_r_awd_sX3TvbZCMJRKQ" target="_blank">Obihai VOIP router on Amazon</a> for $40 to get started.  If your home network doesn&#8217;t have an extra ethernet port, you there&#8217;s a version with an integrated router.</p>
<figure id="attachment_155" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter" style="width: 310px"><a href="http://markfern.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/IMG_20150930_121139.jpg"><img class="size-medium wp-image-155" src="http://markfern.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/IMG_20150930_121139-300x225.jpg" alt="markfern.me" width="300" height="225" srcset="http://markfern.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/IMG_20150930_121139-300x225.jpg 300w, http://markfern.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/IMG_20150930_121139-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a><figcaption class="caption wp-caption-text">Obihai VOIP Router</figcaption></figure>
<p dir="ltr">Here are the rest of the steps:</p>
<p> <a href="http://markfern.me/2015/09/voip-at-home-and-250-in-your-pocket/#more-152" class="more-link"><span aria-label="Continue reading VOIP at Home and $250 in your pocket.">(more&hellip;)</span></a></p>

				<p><a class="btn btn-default read-more" href="http://markfern.me/2015/09/voip-at-home-and-250-in-your-pocket/" title="VOIP at Home and $250 in your pocket.">Read More</a></p>

							</div><!-- .entry-content -->
					</div>
	</div>
