<article id="post-124" class="post-124 post type-post status-publish format-image hentry category-audio post_format-post-format-image">
	<div class="blog-item-wrap">
				<a href="http://markfern.me/2015/06/streaming-stereo-for-half-the-price-of-a-sonos-and-twice-the-value/" title="Streaming Stereo for half the price of a Sonos." >
			 				</a>
		<div class="post-inner-content">
			<header class="entry-header page-header">

				<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://markfern.me/2015/06/streaming-stereo-for-half-the-price-of-a-sonos-and-twice-the-value/" rel="bookmark">Streaming Stereo for half the price of a Sonos.</a></h1>

								<div class="entry-meta">
					<span class="posted-on"><i class="fa fa-calendar"></i> <a href="http://markfern.me/2015/06/streaming-stereo-for-half-the-price-of-a-sonos-and-twice-the-value/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2015-06-17T13:49:05+00:00">June 17, 2015</time><time class="updated" datetime="2015-06-17T14:39:04+00:00">June 17, 2015</time></a></span><span class="byline"> <i class="fa fa-user"></i> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://markfern.me/author/fernmark/">Mark</a></span></span>				<span class="comments-link"><i class="fa fa-comment-o"></i><a href="http://markfern.me/2015/06/streaming-stereo-for-half-the-price-of-a-sonos-and-twice-the-value/#respond">Leave a comment</a></span>
				
				
				</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
							</header><!-- .entry-header -->

						<div class="entry-content">

				<p><a href="http://markfern.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/IMG_20150226_110536.jpg"><img class=" size-medium wp-image-127 alignnone" src="http://markfern.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/IMG_20150226_110536-300x169.jpg" alt="Chinese Amp" width="300" height="169" srcset="http://markfern.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/IMG_20150226_110536-300x169.jpg 300w, http://markfern.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/IMG_20150226_110536-1024x575.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a>      <a href="http://markfern.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/chromecast-dongle.png"><img class=" size-medium wp-image-132 alignnone" src="http://markfern.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/chromecast-dongle-300x169.png" alt="chromecast-dongle" width="300" height="169" srcset="http://markfern.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/chromecast-dongle-300x169.png 300w, http://markfern.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/chromecast-dongle.png 740w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></p>
<p>As a DIY-er, I find spending oodles of cash on things like <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B003CP0FUU/ref=amb_link_432719222_10?pf_rd_m=ATVPDKIKX0DER&amp;pf_rd_s=product-alert&amp;pf_rd_r=128EEJHHFXME33FWKJY0&amp;pf_rd_t=201&amp;pf_rd_p=2105492982&amp;pf_rd_i=B005441AJC" target="_blank">Sonos</a> is wasteful.  If you have the cash and simply don&#8217;t want to bother learning or considering alternatives, I can see how a single system box might be attractive.  Be ready to replace the entire system in a few years when you want to expand or change something.  Stereos, however, have been around since the time of our ancestors, and that maturity makes them fairly fool-proof and inexpensive.  The only thing Sonos adds is streaming and a digital interface.  Here&#8217;s an alternative system that does the exact same thing for half the retail cost of a single-speaker Sonos.  Note: like the Sonos, my system assumes you have wifi and internet.  <a href="http://markfern.me/2015/06/streaming-stereo-for-half-the-price-of-a-sonos-and-twice-the-value/#more-124" class="more-link"><span aria-label="Continue reading Streaming Stereo for half the price of a Sonos.">(more&hellip;)</span></a></p>

				<p><a class="btn btn-default read-more" href="http://markfern.me/2015/06/streaming-stereo-for-half-the-price-of-a-sonos-and-twice-the-value/" title="Streaming Stereo for half the price of a Sonos.">Read More</a></p>

							</div><!-- .entry-content -->
					</div>
	</div>
